    <media alt="A sample brochure is shown with an open pane at the right listing these options for selection: Cut, Copy, Paste Options, Edit Picture, Change Picture, Group, Bring to Front, Send to Back, Link, Save as Picture, Insert Caption, Wrap Text, and Edit Alt Text. Change Picture is selected.">
