    <media alt="A sample brochure is visible. The Document Formatting command group is visible across the top (includes Themes, Colors, Fonts, Paragraph spacing, Effects, and Set as Default). Colors is selected and opens to these options for selection: Custom (shows two different brown color palettes labeled Custom 1 and Custom 2) and Office (lists a variety of color palettes with labels. The Blue Warm palette is selected (includes black and various shades of blue and gray).">
