    <para id="para-00027">To create a flyer, choose a flyer template from Microsoft’s templates, and follow the same steps as for creating a brochure. As you can see in <link target-id="fig-00013"/>, flyer templates are just one, single page, meant to be printed single-sided on one sheet of paper.</para>
    <figure id="fig-00013" class="scaled-down">
    <media alt="A sample flyer is shown with space for a title and subtitle, images, headings, flyer text, and contact information. The flyer has pre-set spacing, font, and design elements included.">
